text: "Unforgettable" is a hip-hop song by French Montana featuring Swae Lee. It was released on April 7, 2017. It is from French Montana's second studio album, Jungle Rules. The song peaked at number 3 on the US Billboard Hot 100. It is French Montana's first song as a lead artist to reach the Top 10, and his first successful song. The music video for the song has over 1.4 billion views on YouTube. ==References== Category:2017 songs Category:Swae Lee songs Category:Hip hop songs
